ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of STÉPHANIE PAQUETTE of Montreal, Quebec, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation for the Quebec region, effective November 23, 2023.
